&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2-4 years of experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B.S. in Public Relations, Communications, or a related field&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interest in financial services, professional services, technology and/or B2B communications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Cision, Factiva, and Microsoft Suite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
